<p><b>REPORT TO THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY ON THE SECOND SESSION 
OF THE HUMAN RIGHTS COUNCIL</b>*<b> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Vice-President and Rapporteur:  Mr. Musa Burayzat (Jordan) 
</b></p>
<p>                                                 
</p>
<p>*  The format of the present report is based on the agenda and &#8220;draft framework for a programme 
of work&#8221; for the second session as adopted by the Council in its decision 1/105 of 30 June 2006.  
It should therefore not serve as a precedent for future sessions of the Council. </p>

