Bahrain (on behalf of the Group of Arab States) formally moved to adjourn the consideration of 
draft resolution A/HRC/2/L.38/Rev.1, as well as that of draft resolution A/HRC/2/L.40/Rev.1 
(see also paragraph 236 below) and draft decision A/HRC/2/L.42/Rev.1 (see also paragraph 241 
below), to the following day, and requested a vote on the motion. 
